        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "SLO budget (0.1%)" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "fixedColor": "red", "mode": "fixed" } }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 7 },
      "id": 6,
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "entain:sli:error:ratio",
          "legendFormat": "5xx error ratio"
        },
        {
          "expr": "0.001",
          "legendFormat": "SLO budget (0.1%)"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Error Budget (SLA signal)",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "custom": { "drawStyle": "line", "fillOpacity": 10, "lineWidth": 2 },
          "unit": "s"
        }
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 7 },
      "id": 7,
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.50, sum(rate(entain_http_request_duration_seconds_bucket[1m])) by (le))",
          "legendFormat": "p50"
        },
        {
          "expr": "entain:sli:latency:p95_seconds",
          "legendFormat": "p95"
        },
        {
          "expr": "entain:sli:latency:p99_seconds",
          "legendFormat": "p99"
        },
        {
          "expr": "0.1",
          "legendFormat": "SLO line (100ms)"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Latency percentiles vs SLO",
      "type": "timeseries"
    },
    {
      "collapsed": false,
      "gridPos": { "h": 1, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 15 },
      "id": 8,
      "title": "Transparency — service health vs business outcomes",
      "type": "row"
    },
    {
      "gridPos": { "h": 3, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 16 },
      "id": 13,
      "options": {
        "code": { "language": "plaintext", "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "**How to read:** green `200` / `applied` = healthy. **Orange/blue 4xx** and `duplicate` / `insufficient_funds` = **business errors** (service is fine, rules fired). **Red 5xx** and `internal` = **service degradation** (bug or infra). Under `make load-25` almost everything is 200 — check the stat panels below: zeros on 402/409 are informative too.",
        "mode": "markdown"
      },
      "title": "Legend",
      "type": "text"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "5xx and internal = broken service. Should stay at 0 under normal load.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 3,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.001 }
            ]
          },
          "unit": "reqps"
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "5xx HTTP" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "displayName", "value": "5xx HTTP" }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "internal (metric)" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "displayName", "value": "internal (metric)" }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 19 },
      "id": 14,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "orientation": "horizontal",
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"] },
        "textMode": "value_and_name"
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(entain_http_requests_total{status=~\"5..\"}[1m])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "5xx HTTP",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "sum(rate(entain_transactions_rejected_total{reason=\"internal\"}[1m])) or vector(0)",
          "legendFormat": "internal (metric)",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ],
      "title": "SERVICE DEGRADATION",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "description": "4xx and tx rejections = expected rule-based failures, not service outage.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "decimals": 2,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "blue", "value": null },
              { "color": "orange", "value": 1 }
